02:54:51.671 --> 02:54:53.923
how do you want to do this?

02:54:53.923 --> 02:54:56.349
(cheering)

02:54:56.349 --> 02:54:58.252
TRAVIS: First one!

02:54:58.252 --> 02:54:59.677
SAM: First blood.

02:54:59.677 --> 02:55:06.197
MARISHA: I'll do the uppercut with the other one,
