03:04:47.146 --> 03:04:49.374
MARISHA: What's your name, man?

03:04:49.374 --> 03:04:55.259
TALIESIN: Wow, he's really shook up.

03:04:55.259 --> 03:04:56.842
SAM: Jamieson.

